<section id="action" aria-labelledby="action-heading">
	<div class="section-label">What Now</div>
	<h2 id="action-heading" class="manifesto-title">Organise.<br />Educate.<br />Act.</h2>
	<p class="manifesto-intro">
		Knowledge without action is complicity. The data is clear. The system
		will not dismantle itself. These are starting points — not endpoints.
	</p>
	<div class="action-grid">
		<div class="action-column reveal">
			<h3>Organisations &amp; Movements</h3>
			<ul class="action-list">
				<li><a href="https://saftu.org.za" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SAFTU</a> — South African Federation of Trade Unions</li>
				<li><a href="https://www.equaleducation.org.za" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Equal Education</a> — Education justice and school infrastructure</li>
				<li><a href="https://groundwork.org.za" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">groundWork</a> — Environmental justice, coal, and Eskom accountability</li>
				<li><a href="https://nu.org.za" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ndifuna Ukwazi</a> — Cape Town housing and land justice</li>
				<li><a href="https://www.blacksash.org.za" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Black Sash</a> — Social grants, welfare rights, and SASSA accountability</li>
				<li><a href="https://cer.org.za" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Centre for Environmental Rights</a> — Legal advocacy on mining and environmental harm</li>
				<li><a href="https://pmbejd.org.za" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">PMBEJD</a> — Pietermaritzburg Economic Justice &amp; Dignity Group</li>
				<li><a href="https://taxjustice.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tax Justice Network</a> — Global and Africa-focused tax justice research</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="action-column reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.1s">
			<h3>Essential Reading</h3>
			<ul class="action-list">
				<li><a href="https://www.versobooks.com/products/2647-how-europe-underdeveloped-africa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>How Europe Underdeveloped Africa</em></a> — Walter Rodney</li>
				<li><a href="https://groveatlantic.com/book/the-wretched-of-the-earth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>The Wretched of the Earth</em></a> — Frantz Fanon</li>
				<li><a href="https://www.jasonhickel.org/the-divide" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>The Divide</em></a> — Jason Hickel</li>
				<li><a href="https://www.plutobooks.com/9780745317694/elite-transition/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>Elite Transition</em></a> — Patrick Bond</li>
				<li><a href="https://www.bloomsbury.com/us/south-africa-pushed-to-the-limit-9781848134201/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>South Africa Pushed to the Limit</em></a> — Hein Marais</li>
				<li><a href="https://gabriel-zucman.eu/hidden-wealth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>The Hidden Wealth of Nations</em></a> — Gabriel Zucman</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="action-column reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.2s">
			<h3>What You Can Do</h3>
			<ul class="action-list">
				<li>Join your union — or organise to form one</li>
				<li>Support housing rights organisations and anti-eviction campaigns</li>
				<li>Demand NHI implementation and public healthcare investment</li>
				<li>Engage your ward councillor on service delivery accountability</li>
				<li>Demand Eskom reform and a just energy transition out of coal</li>
				<li>Share the data — this site is open-source</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="action-stamp" aria-hidden="true">
		THE CRISES ARE THE SAME CRISIS.<br />THE SOLUTION IS THE SAME SOLUTION.
	</div>
</section>
